What is require?
A condition checker. If condition is false → function stops and shows error.

Syntax :
         require(condition, "error message");

 How it works :
     condition true → function continues ✅
     condition false → function stops + error ❌

Common UseCase :
    require(amount > 0, "Amount must be greater than 0");
    require(amount <= balance, "Insufficient balance"); 
    require(isActive == true, "Not active");
    require(quantity <= stock, "Not enough stock");
    require(revenue > cost, "No profit");

Key points :
   Always write require before the logic
   Multiple requires allowed in one function
   Stops early if condition fails — saves gas












